the good knowledge of God. 2 Chron. 30. 22. He did also appoint<lb/>
the people to Minister sustenance unto them. 2 Chron. 31. <lb/>
4. He appointed his own portion. Moreover he commanded<lb/>
the people to give the portion of the Priests that they might<lb/>
