1. <notvariant>Ob</notvariant>. If Magistrates may not impose, nor <normalised orig="compell" auto="true">compel</normalised> to a <choice ana="illegible">
                     <sic>Ch*r*</sic>
                     <corr>Charity</corr>
                  </choice>
                  <lb/>
