Sol. No, toleration is taken away by his act of restraining;<lb/>
That which I <normalised orig="restraine" auto="true">restrain</normalised>, I do not tolerate, he that <normalised orig="restraines" auto="true">restrains</normalised> the<lb/>
practice of Idolatry, the spreading of Heresies, &amp;c. cannot <choice ana="illegible">
                     <sic>*e</sic>
                     <corr>be</corr>
