                     <sic>b*</sic>
                     <corr><normalised orig="bee" auto="true">be</normalised></corr>
                  </choice>
                  <lb/>
that Christian moderation which should be known to all men.<lb/>
3. <notvariant>Ob</notvariant>. But must such dissenters as refuse to act according<lb/>
