Sol. No: there is a twofold remedy provided. 1. One <normalised orig="spirituall" auto="true">spiritual</normalised><lb/>
for the healing and reducing of persons going <choice ana="illegible">
                     <sic>astray*</sic>
                     <corr>astrayn</corr>
