                     <sic>appl*e*</sic>
                     <corr>applied</corr>
                  </choice>
                  <lb/>
through Gods blessing will cure <normalised orig="spirituall" auto="true">spiritual</normalised> diseases. 2. But if <choice ana="illegible">
                     <sic>n*</sic>
                     <corr>not</corr>
                  </choice>
